<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">今天（12月13日），是第12个南京大屠杀死难者国家公祭日。88年前的今天，侵华日军野蛮侵入南京，制造了惨绝人寰的南京大屠杀惨案。这份民族伤痛，我们从未忘记。今天，以国之名祭奠遇难同胞，铭记历史，吾辈自强！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975589014.png" alt="1765975589014.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975589014.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975609808.png" alt="1765975609808.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975609808.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975622607.png" alt="1765975622607.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975622607.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975634684.png" alt="1765975634684.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975634684.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975648575.png" alt="1765975648575.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975648575.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975659222.png" alt="1765975659222.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975659222.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975669522.png" alt="1765975669522.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975669522.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975679962.png" alt="1765975679962.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765975679962.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><br></p>